172 A.3d 1081 NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. J.D., JR., DEFENDANT-PETITIONER, AND J.G., DEFENDANT. IN THE MATTER OF J.D., III, A MINOR-RESPONDENT.

C-268 September Term 2017

078479 November 2, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in [ A-XXXXXX-XX ] having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
